<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>About Us - StudentEz</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/navbar.css" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/about.css" />
</head>
<body>
  {{> navbar}}

  <div class="about-container">
    <h1 class="main-heading">👋 About StudentEz — Your College Companion</h1>
    <p class="intro">
      Welcome to <strong>StudentEz</strong> — a smart, all-in-one student dashboard built to simplify your academic and career journey.
      College life is busy, and we’re here to make it easier.
    </p>

    <div class="feature-card">
      <h2>💼 Job Portal</h2>
      <p>Apply to internships and jobs with ease. Our job portal lets you:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>🔎 Discover job listings posted by admins</li>
        <li>📤 Apply with your resume</li>
        <li>📊 Track your application status (Pending, Accepted, Declined)</li>
        <li>📝 Receive notes or feedback from recruiters</li>
        <li>❌ Delete your applications if needed</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-card">
      <h2>🎓 Workshop Portal</h2>
      <p>Explore hands-on learning opportunities beyond the classroom:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>📅 Browse all upcoming workshops with images and details</li>
        <li>🧠 Learn new skills and boost your profile</li>
        <li>✅ Enroll in a click, view your enrollments, or unenroll anytime</li>
        <li>📈 Admins can manage and view participants seamlessly</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-card">
      <h2>📄 Resume Screener</h2>
      <p>Before your resume reaches recruiters, make it ATS-friendly:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>🎯 Score out of 100 based on real ATS standards</li>
        <li>📌 Keyword matching, action verbs, formatting & length feedback</li>
        <li>🛠 Suggestions to improve sections and boost your chances</li>
        <li>📃 Metrics like page count and word count included</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <hr/>

    <h2 class="section-heading">📚 Academic & Personal Trackers</h2>

    <div class="grid-trackers">
      <div class="tracker-card">
        <h3>📊 Attendance Tracker</h3>
        <p>Set your attendance goal, mark daily presence, and see how many classes you can miss or must attend.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="tracker-card">
        <h3>📝 Exam Planner</h3>
        <p>Add upcoming exams, include links, tips, and questions. Stay organized and revision-ready.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="tracker-card">
        <h3>💰 Budget Tracker</h3>
        <p>Set your monthly budget, log expenses by category, and view suggestions based on your savings or spending.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="tracker-card">
        <h3>📅 Study Planner</h3>
        <p>Create date-wise study tasks, mark them complete, and filter by day to stay focused and productive.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
